  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/79193ad537f7680464f8f6071589b95b.poster.avif?t=1774434927\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/79193ad537f7680464f8f6071589b95b.webm?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/79193ad537f7680464f8f6071589b95b.mp4?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple upgradable characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced twin-stick shooting and melee combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create outlandish weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destructible scenery</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrades, abilities, skill trees, and MORE! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crazed AI robot Gods!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RAGNAROK ROGUELITE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/c4d51035de6f7d12aaaa36037670dca6.poster.avif?t=1774434927\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/c4d51035de6f7d12aaaa36037670dca6.webm?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/c4d51035de6f7d12aaaa36037670dca6.mp4?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try, die and try again!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up, amass firepower & hone your skills to fight your way through the post-apocalyptic Viking future and take down Odin!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SPECIAL ABILITIES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/2e88f9f61c0e44dd649e07f307a42c51.poster.avif?t=1774434927\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/2e88f9f61c0e44dd649e07f307a42c51.webm?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/2e88f9f61c0e44dd649e07f307a42c51.mp4?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade characters with unique skill trees and unlock new skins & customisations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Punch gods in the face with your robot arm as the Cyberserker. Slice your way through mobs with the Dark Elf. Stampede your foes as a Viking Moose. Mine gold to upgrade your gear as the Dwarf, or dual wield miniguns twice your size as the manic Gnome. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BUILD YOUR OWN FIREPOWER</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/bdc018acf7565f062e0496849274b59c.poster.avif?t=1774434927\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/bdc018acf7565f062e0496849274b59c.webm?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/bdc018acf7565f062e0496849274b59c.mp4?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want a minigun that shoots homing bullets covered in acid that heals you?... You got that!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want a crossbow that shoots 7 arrows at once, bounces around corners and freezes enemies?... You can do that!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want a giant fork to… fork things?… Ok, I guess… You do you…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GIANT BOSSES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/11e378decd2a1233a4f5bfb2b99878c3.poster.avif?t=1774434927\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/11e378decd2a1233a4f5bfb2b99878c3.webm?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/11e378decd2a1233a4f5bfb2b99878c3.mp4?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Odin isn't your only problem! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take down huge wolves, ice giants, ancient Vikings and possessed greatswords! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SURVIVE THE HORDES</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/c01af44c75b8fe5ccd02cc7c91db99bf.poster.avif?t=1774434927\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/c01af44c75b8fe5ccd02cc7c91db99bf.webm?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/c01af44c75b8fe5ccd02cc7c91db99bf.mp4?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the endless Viking hordes in the arena to test your skills and unlock the best weapons… can you make it out alive? </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/79193ad537f7680464f8f6071589b95b.poster.avif?t=1774434927\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/79193ad537f7680464f8f6071589b95b.webm?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/79193ad537f7680464f8f6071589b95b.mp4?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple upgradable characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced twin-stick shooting and melee combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create outlandish weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destructible scenery</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrades, abilities, skill trees, and MORE! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crazed AI robot Gods!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RAGNAROK ROGUELITE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/c4d51035de6f7d12aaaa36037670dca6.poster.avif?t=1774434927\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/c4d51035de6f7d12aaaa36037670dca6.webm?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/c4d51035de6f7d12aaaa36037670dca6.mp4?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try, die and try again!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up, amass firepower & hone your skills to fight your way through the post-apocalyptic Viking future and take down Odin!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SPECIAL ABILITIES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/2e88f9f61c0e44dd649e07f307a42c51.poster.avif?t=1774434927\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/2e88f9f61c0e44dd649e07f307a42c51.webm?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/2e88f9f61c0e44dd649e07f307a42c51.mp4?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade characters with unique skill trees and unlock new skins & customisations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Punch gods in the face with your robot arm as the Cyberserker. Slice your way through mobs with the Dark Elf. Stampede your foes as a Viking Moose. Mine gold to upgrade your gear as the Dwarf, or dual wield miniguns twice your size as the manic Gnome. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BUILD YOUR OWN FIREPOWER</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/bdc018acf7565f062e0496849274b59c.poster.avif?t=1774434927\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/bdc018acf7565f062e0496849274b59c.webm?t=1774434