ts/steam/apps/2154240/extras/c01af44c75b8fe5ccd02cc7c91db99bf.webm?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154240/extras/c01af44c75b8fe5ccd02cc7c91db99bf.mp4?t=1774434927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the endless Viking hordes in the arena to test your skills and unlock the best weapons… can you make it out alive? </p>",
